Executive Profile
Thomas B. Michaud  President and CEO of Keefe, Bruyette & Woods, Stifel Financial Corp.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships53$4,523,183As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Thomas B. Michaud, also known as Tom, has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of KBW LLC (alternate name, KBW Inc.) since October 27, 2011 and 2006 respectively. Mr. Michaud has been Chief Executive Officer of Keefe, Bruyette, & Woods, Inc. since October 27, 2011 and has been its President since 2006. Mr. Michaud served as Senior Vice President of Stifel Financial Corp. since February 15, 2013. He served as Chief Operating Officer of Keefe, Bruyette, & ... Woods, Inc. from 2001 to 2011. He served as the Chief Operating Officer of KBW LLC since 2001. At KBW LLC, he was responsible for the sales and trading business including equities and fixed income. He was responsible for sales and trading business including equities and fixed income of KBW. Mr. Michaud began his career at KBW LLC in 1986 as a Member of Bank Watch Department and also served it's Research Department. He joined Equity Sales in 1988. He served as an Executive Vice-President and Director of Equity Sales of KBW since 1999. He served as the Chairman of Keefe, Bruyette, & Woods, Inc. since October 27, 2011. He serves as Vice Chairman of Keefe, Bruyette, & Woods, Inc. He served as Vice Chairman of KBW LLC since August 1, 2005. He has been a Director of Keefe, Bruyette & Woods, Inc. since 1999. He has been a Director of KBW LLC since 1999. He serves as a Director of the Greenwich Chapter of American Red Cross. He served as a Director of Stifel Financial Corp. since February 15, 2013 until June 6, 2017. He served as a Member of the Representative Town Meeting of Town of Greenwich, Connecticut from 1994 to 2001. Mr. Michaud is a Graduate of Middlebury College and earned an MBA from the Stern School of Business at New York University.Read Full Background




